pitch:
The CoinWealth Platform will bridge the gap between the traditional investor and crypto-investing.

Founded by veterans from the investment industry, the Platform will bring more structure to the investment process and help investors avoid the pitfalls that are unique to the Crypto segment.

Expected date of Public launch of the platform is 1st March 2022. Integrations are underway with different crypto exchanges.

It takes a village to seek, research, track and find the right crypto assets for different crypto portfolio needs.  And, it takes an understanding of the traditional investor to help them along in the journey of diversifying into crypto assets.

Crypto-markets are open 24/7 with over 250+ exchanges worldwide.

We have derived a unique approach of crypto-investing by rigorously evaluating the following:

	‚Ä¢ Understanding the real-world use-cases and traction of blockchain projects;
	‚Ä¢ Project release cycle, tokenomics & supply changes of cryptos;
	‚Ä¢ On-chain metrics & shift between long and short-term holders;
	‚Ä¢ Volatility, segmentation and other signatures of different projects;
	‚Ä¢ Domination % and the consequent impact on visibility;
	‚Ä¢ Establishing research sources and data sets that are unique to Crypto;
	‚Ä¢ High cash-to-holdings ratios & higher rates of rebalance.
	‚Ä¢ Tracking growth of the ecosystems in which the crypto operates in and segment health.

Our team works on ensuring that all of the above factors are ranked on a scorecard, fundamentals verified and news streams checked before picking the most promising projects or investments. We then package them into products that traditional investors - retail, corporate or enterprise are familiar with bridging the gap between the two.
